docs.title: Our Pledge
docs.text: We pledge to make participation in our project a harassment-free experience for everyone.

docs.title: Our Standards
docs.text:
Examples of behavior that contributes to a positive environment: - Using welcoming and inclusive language - Being respectful of differing viewpoints

Examples of unacceptable behavior: - Trolling, insulting comments - Personal or political attacks

docs.title: Enforcement
docs.text:
Instances of abusive behavior may be reported to the project maintainers at [your email].

This Code of Conduct is adapted from the Contributor Covenant.
